commit 2fcba17fc4d7eda8fc60567169cf2a0e6fcfb2f8
Author: Jia Tan <jiat0218@gmail.com>
Date:   2022-12-29 01:55:19 +0800

    xz: Includes <time.h> and <sys/time.h> conditionally in mytime.c.
    
