commit db465419ae26ec7fb9b9472183911ff521620c77
Author: Lasse Collin <lasse.collin@tukaani.org>
Date:   2021-01-17 19:20:50 +0200

    liblzma: In EROFS LZMA decoder, verify that comp_size matches at the end.
    
